{"type":"message","id":"bb8ea616","parentId":"c8f35d2a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:42:02.179Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bcbd49174b7142dfa76b1fdb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n2、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n3、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 3.1、满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 3.2、只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n4、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n5、使用openclaw cron创建一个5s后执行的一次性隔离定时任务，将数据通过飞书渠道推送给ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5用户；\n6、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773067322178}}
{"type":"message","id":"074a91db","parentId":"bb8ea616","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:42:04.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据 cron 任务要求，我需要先查看 get-data-template.md、alert-rules.md 和 alert-template.md 这几个相关文件来了解数据获取格式、预警规则和推送模板。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我读取相关的参考文件来完成这个任务。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fe5c7801043046bc804a9771","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7aabfc1737be42858beec8fb","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2a4a42fac95c4f2d89c335c7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773067322179}}
{"type":"message","id":"513dbbcd","parentId":"074a91db","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:42:04.693Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fe5c7801043046bc804a9771","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773067324691}}
{"type":"message","id":"e659c006","parentId":"513dbbcd","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:42:04.695Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7aabfc1737be42858beec8fb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n规则条目：\n\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773067324694}}
{"type":"message","id":"40920640","parentId":"e659c006","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:42:04.698Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2a4a42fac95c4f2d89c335c7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773067324697}}
