{"type":"message","id":"9b4aa2e4","parentId":"13d02e5c","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:43:50.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从浏览器快照中提取了第一只股票的数据后，需要创建一个 Python 脚本来自动获取所有自选股数据并保存到文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！我现在可以从同花顺的页面提取数据。从页面信息可以看到：\n- 中国石油 (601857): 价格 12.92 元，涨跌幅 +5.04%，涨跌额 +0.62 元\n\n让我创建一个脚本批量获取所有股票的实时数据：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b6b1e73245b84cff99d57096","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Get all stocks real-time data from 10jqka and save to realtime-data.txt\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport time\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\nimport urllib.request\n\nWATCHLIST_FILE = \"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt\"\nOUTPUT_FILE = \"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\"\n\ndef fetch_stock_data(code, name):\n    \"\"\"从同花顺页面获取股票数据\"\"\"\n    try:\n        url = f\"https://stockpage.10jqka.com.cn/{code}/\"\n        \n        req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={\n            'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36',\n            'Accept': 'text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8',\n            'Accept-Language': 'zh-CN,zh;q=0.9,en;q=0.8',\n        })\n        \n        with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=15) as response:\n            html = response.read().decode('utf-8')\n            \n            # 使用 BeautifulSoup 解析\n            soup = BeautifulSoup(html, 'html.parser')\n            \n            # 查找当前价 - 在 iframe 中查找\n            price = None\n            change_pct = None\n            \n            # 尝试多种方式获取价格\n            # 方式 1: 查找包含价格的强标签\n            strong_tags = soup.find_all('strong')\n            for strong in strong_tags:\n                text = strong.get_text(strip=True)\n                if re.match(r'^\\d+\\.\\d{2}$', text) and float(text) > 0 and float(text) < 10000:\n                    # 验证是否为合理价格范围\n                    price = float(text)\n                    break\n            \n            # 如果没找到价格，继续搜索\n            if not price:\n                # 查看整个页面的文本内容，寻找数字模式\n                page_text = soup.get_text()\n                import re\n                matches = re.findall(r'\\b(\\d+\\.\\d{2})\\b', page_text)\n                for m in matches:\n                    val = float(m)\n                    if 1 <= val <= 5000:  # 合理的股票价格范围\n                        price = val\n                        break\n            \n            # 获取涨跌幅\n            change_pct_match = re.search(r'([\\+-]?\\d+\\.\\d+)%', page_text)\n            if change_pct_match:\n                change_pct = float(change_pct_match.group(1))\n            \n            # 获取时间戳\n            timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n            \n            return {\n                'code': code,\n                'name': name,\n                'price': price,\n                'change_pct': change_pct,\n                'timestamp': timestamp\n            }\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ {code} {name}: 获取失败 - {str(e)[:50]}\")\n        return None\n    \n    import re\n    return None\n\n# 读取自选股\nstocks = []\nwith open(WATCHLIST_FILE, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    for line in f:\n        line = line.strip()\n        if line and '|' in line:\n            parts = line.split('|')\n            code = parts[0].strip()\n            name = parts[1].strip() if len(parts) > 1 else code\n            stocks.append((code, name))\n\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(\"老板自选股实时行情数据采集\")\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\n\nresults = []\nfor i, (code, name) in enumerate(stocks, 1):\n    print(f\"[{i}/{len(stocks)}] 正在获取 {code} - {name}...\")\n    \n    result = fetch_stock_data(code, name)\n    \n    if result and result['price'] and result['change_pct']:\n        results.append(result)\n        sign = '+' if result['change_pct'] >= 0 else ''\n        print(f\"  ✅ ¥{result['price']:.2f} ({sign}{result['change_pct']:.2f}%)\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  ⚠️ 数据获取失败\")\n    \n    time.sleep(2)\n\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 70)\nprint(f\"完成！共获取 {len(results)} 条有效数据\")\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\n\n# 按涨跌幅绝对值排序（从高到低）\nsorted_results = sorted(results, key=lambda x: abs(x['change_pct']), reverse=True)\n\n# 写入输出文件\nwith open(OUTPUT_FILE, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(\"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间 |\\n\")\n    f.write(\"|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\\n\")\n    \n    for r in sorted_results:\n        # 计算昨收价和涨跌额\n        prev_close = r['price'] / (1 + r['change_pct'] / 100) if r['change_pct'] != 0 else r['price']\n        price_change = r['price'] - prev_close\n        \n        sign = '+' if r['change_pct'] >= 0 else ''\n        time_str = r['timestamp'].split()[1] if ' ' in r['timestamp'] else \"N/A\"\n        \n        f.write(f\"| {r['code']} | {r['name']} | ¥{r['price']:.2f} | {sign}{r['change_pct']:.2f}% | ¥{price_change:.2f} | {time_str} |\\n\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n✅ 数据已保存到 {OUTPUT_FILE}\")\nprint(f\"📊 共收集到 {len(results)} 条实时行情数据\")\n","file_path":"/tmp/get_stocks_realtime.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773067416972}}
