{"type":"message","id":"3bb0ecdb","parentId":"b6419d03","timestamp":"2026-03-09T14:44:43.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"既然网页方式太慢，我应该直接使用 Python 的 urllib 库来快速获取所有股票数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我创建一个更简单的方法，直接通过浏览器抓取几个关键股票的页面快照：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0032d712ebf24f1880427c94","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport urllib.request\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\ndef get_stock(code):\n    url = f'https://stockpage.10jqka.com.cn/{code}/'\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'})\n    with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=10) as resp:\n        html = resp.read().decode('utf-8', errors='ignore')\n    \n    # 搜索价格和涨跌幅\n    import re\n    \n    # 查找价格 (通常是 x.xx 格式)\n    prices = re.findall(r'\\\"price\\\":(\\d+\\.?\\d*)', html)\n    price = float(prices[0]) if prices else None\n    \n    # 查找涨跌幅  \n    changes = re.findall(r'pct_chg\\\":(-?\\d+\\.?\\d*)', html)\n    pct = float(changes[0]) if changes else None\n    \n    return {'price': price, 'pct': pct}\n\n# 读取 watchlist\nwith open('/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt', 'r') as f:\n    lines = [l.strip() for l in f.readlines() if l.strip()]\n\nresults = []\nfor line in lines[:5]:  # 只抓前几只作为示例\n    parts = line.split('|')\n    code, name = parts[0], parts[1] if len(parts)>1 else ''\n    try:\n        data = get_stock(code)\n        if data['price'] and data['pct']:\n            results.append((code, name, data['price'], data['pct']))\n            print(f'{code} {name}: ¥{data[\\\"price\\\"]:.2f} ({data[\\\"pct\\\"]:+.2f}%)')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{code} 失败：{e}')\n\nprint(f'\\n共获取 {len(results)} 条数据')\n\" 2>&1 | head -20\n","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773067466291}}
